snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - The Angels Of Death
snippet.description:
Pre-order Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 now: https://t.ly/tFf5Z

We are the Emperor's Angels. We are the Space Marines.
Answer the call of War on September 9th.

Only a few days left before the Early Unlock, 4 days before the full release, are we ready Brothers? ⚔️
